divs: Sighting DetailsHere's some more photos I took today around 3:30PM just aiming at the sky in all directions. Almost all 75 pictures have objects in them but I will post only a few of the good ones. The first I counted over 55 objects in the picture looking towards the west the same area of the sky where I took many other pictures. I'm also including the original so whoever wants to dabble with the photo to see how many objects I missed feel free to do so. This is an incredible event happening here and I hope to get more photos. I'll post Part 4 after this one with three more pictures then I need to take a break as this has overwhelmed me. All I want to say is the Human Race has to take a good look at itself and to learn the things that are the most important here with their time on this Planet. 1 Your Spiritual Awareness God, Jesus Christ, The Holy Spirit, Angels 2 To LOVE everything, as we are all made up of the same energy 3 To stop destroying this Planet with our Pollution, Poverty, and Politics! 4 To realize that we are not the only intelligent life forms that exist. Thanks JC
